en:
In a hamlet, in the middle of the countryside, this large and cosy house located in the heart of a farm will make families happy

It is also an ideal situation for nature and fishing lovers who will be able to enjoy their passion in the peace and quiet... the Bresle river is close to the property

It is adapted for people with reduced mobility.

È adattato alle persone con mobilità ridotta.

Está adaptado para personas con movilidad reducida.
